title: Navigate forwards into to a grid
instructions: Starting at the 'Navigate forwards from here' link, navigate into the grid.
assertions: roleGrid nameTransactionsJanuary1ThroughJanuary6 numberColumns5 numberRows7 firstColumnHeaderContentDate coordinatesColumnHeaderColumn1Row1

title: Navigate backwards into a grid
instructions: Starting at the 'Navigate backwards from here' link, navigate into the grid.
assertions: roleGrid gridBoundary nameTransactionsJanuary1ThroughJanuary6 numberColumns5 numberRows7 lastColumnHeaderContentBalance lastCellContent99553200 coordinatesLastCellColumn5Row7

title: Move focus forwards into a grid
instructions: Starting at the 'Navigate forwards from here' link, , move keyboard focus onto the '01-Jan-16' cell
assertions: roleGrid nameTransactionsJanuary1ThroughJanuary6 numberColumns5 numberRows7 firstColumnHeaderContentDate firstCellContent01Jan16 coordinatesFirstCellColumn1Row2

title: Move focus backwards into a grid
instructions: Starting at the 'Navigate backwards from here' link, move keyboard focus onto the first non-header cell in the grid.
assertions: roleGrid nameTransactionsJanuary1ThroughJanuary6 numberColumns5 numberRows7 firstColumnHeaderContentDate firstCellContent01Jan16 coordinatesFirstCellColumn1Row2
